oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Johnson Bible College President Ashley Sidney Johnson and Mrs. Johnson, 1917
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: unknown
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Johnson Bible College President Ashley Sidney Johnson and Mrs. Johnson with G.H. Cacharias who came from Greece and enrolled at Johnson Bible College in 1909 and graduated in 1914. Mr. Cacharias later became the Academic Dean at Minnesota Bible College in Minneapolis, MN. Photograph taken in 1917.
